'''Battlemaster''' was a title held by [[Jedi Master]] [[Cin Drallig]] at the [[Imperial Palace|Jedi Temple]] on [[Coruscant]], concurrently with that of [[Chief of Security]].<ref name="FC" /> Master Drallig was [[Death|killed]] during [[Operation: Knightfall]] as part of the [[Great Jedi Purge]].<ref name="Episode III">{{Film|III}}</ref>

